cos'è?<delay20 /> <anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Tadaaa! <delay8 />Una <colour id="1" />stella filante<colour id="65535" />!</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ehi, <tag a="110" b="3" />! <delay20 />Aspetta solo un secondo.</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ah, <tag a="110" b="3" />! Tempismo perfetto!<delay20 /> <anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Un attimo solo.</message>
